Rating: 4
i love everything in this receipe so decided to try it and wow is it good. i left out the olive oil by mistake and didn't really miss it. i'm interested to try it again without a dump/guess on the measurements so figured out the proportions for 5 servings which is pretty close to what i tried last night and 2 of us ate every bite of it. i think it needs more celery leaves so went heavy on that. generous 1/2 lb sprouts,generous 1/2 tbs vinegar, 1/2 tbs mayo, 2.5 tbs evoo, 2 small or 1 very large apple, 1/2 celery, blue and walnuts. hope this helps and can't wait to try again.

